---

Common Interview Questions

Q1. Which step is the most important?

Analysis.

Collection gathers data, but analysis turns it into actionable intelligence.


---

Q2. Why is feedback important?

Because intelligence improves based on operational validation. If assumptions are incorrect or the environment changes, the reports and recommendations need to be updated.


---

Q3. Is collecting threat feeds enough?

No.

Threat feeds provide raw information. Intelligence requires processing, analysis, and recommendations tailored to your organization.


